      • get

        public static long get(Time time,
       TimeUnit timeUnit)
        Convenience method to measure time in a given TimeUnit.
        参数:
        time - Time instance to use
        timeUnit - TimeUnit to measure in
        返回:
        long measured time in TimeUnit dimension

      • getDiff

        public static long getDiff(Time time,
           TimeUnit timeUnit,
           long startTime)
        Convenience method to get time since the beginning of an event in a given TimeUnit.
        参数:
        time - Time object used for measuring.
        timeUnit - TimeUnit to use for dimension.
        startTime - beginning time to diff against
        返回:
        time elapsed since startTime in TimeUnit dimension.
